The European Investment Bank said it ismaking a 300 mln franc loan to Peugeot SA &lt;PEUP.PA> torestructure the paint works at its Sochaux car factory inFrance.    It said the ten-year loan carries interest at 9.15 pct andfollows a 300 mln franc 8.60 pct ten-year loan the bank made toPeugeot last July.    Work on the paint shop at Sochaux is part of a 1.3 billionfranc operation to modernise the group's factories, it added. REUTER&#3;